{"word":"G593 - ἀποδοκιμάζω - apodokimázō - ap-od-ok-ee-mad'-zo - Disallow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδοκιμάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apodokimázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-od-ok-ee-mad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Disallow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தள்ளு"},{"paragraph":"to disapprove, reject, repudiate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1381 - δοκιμάζω - dokimázō - dok-im-ad'-zo/1381\">G1381</a>; to <i>disapprove</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>repudiate:</i> - disallow, reject.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}